196
00:10:38,890 --> 00:10:42,740
Neither dead nor alive...

197
00:10:42,860 --> 00:10:47,050
I think they can be
called living corpses.

198
00:10:53,150 --> 00:10:54,280
A living corpse like me?

199
00:10:55,780 --> 00:10:56,610
No.

200
00:10:59,130 --> 00:10:59,900
