I’ll handle the dead part.

255
00:13:03,330 --> 00:13:05,000
As for those who are neither dead
nor alive, we will handle it together.

256
00:13:05,350 --> 00:13:06,030
I don’t believe

257
00:13:06,200 --> 00:13:08,230
